coon
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a Pacific Islander. Rarely applied to a Maori: occas. used c1890-1920 in the name of `nigger minstrel' type groups: e.g. Wellington ?date `Karaka Koons'.
